statements: SELECT * FROM ai_model_configurations;
SELECT model_name, model_type FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE model_type = 'classification';
SELECT id, model_name, parameters FROM ai_model_configurations ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT model_type, COUNT(*) AS model_count FROM ai_model_configurations GROUP BY model_type;
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE model_name = 'Linear Regression' AND model_type = 'Regression'
SELECT id, model_name FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE id > 100 ORDER BY id DESC
SELECT model_name, configuration->>'learning_rate' AS learning_rate FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE model_type = 'Neural Network'
SELECT id, model_name, parameters->>'iterations' AS iterations FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE parameters->>'batch_size' = '32'
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_models FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE model_type IN ('Regression', 'Classification')
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configs
SELECT model_name, created_at FROM ai_model_configs ORDER BY created_at DESC
SELECT model_description FROM ai_model_configs WHERE model_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT * FROM ai_model_parameters ORDER BY model_id ASC, parameter_name DESC
SELECT model_name, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM ai_model_configs JOIN ai_model_parameters ON ai_model_configs.model_id = ai_model_parameters.model_id
SELECT model_id, model_name, model_description, created_at FROM ai_model_configs WHERE model_name = 'Linear Regression';
SELECT model_id, model_name, model_description FROM ai_model_configs ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configs LEFT JOIN ai_model_parameters ON ai_model_configs.model_id = ai_model_parameters.model_id;

SELECT model_id, model_name, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM ai_model_configs JOIN ai_model_parameters ON ai_model_configs.model_id = ai_model_parameters.model_id WHERE parameter_name = 'learning_rate';
SELECT model_name, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM ai_model_parameters JOIN ai_model_configs ON ai_model_parameters.model_id = ai_model_configs.model_id ORDER BY parameter_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM model_configurations;
SELECT model_name, configuration_json FROM model_configurations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM model_parameters ORDER BY parameter_name DESC;
SELECT log_message, timestamp FROM model_logs ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT model_name, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM model_configurations JOIN model_parameters ON model_configurations.id = model_parameters.model_id;
SELECT * FROM model_configurations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT model_name, configuration_json FROM model_configurations WHERE model_name = 'model1' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT * FROM model_parameters WHERE parameter_name LIKE '%weight%' AND parameter_value > 0.5;
SELECT model_id, AVG(parameter_value) as avg_value FROM model_parameters GROUP BY model_id HAVING avg_value > 0.3 ORDER BY avg_value DESC;
SELECT model_id, log_message, timestamp FROM model_logs WHERE model_id IN (SELECT id FROM model_configurations WHERE model_name = 'model3') ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configurations;
SELECT model_name, creator_name FROM ai_model_configurations;
SELECT id, model_name, creator_name FROM ai_model_configurations ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT * FROM model_parameters WHERE parameter_value > 0.5;
SELECT id, parameter_name FROM model_parameters ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT * FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE id = 1;
SELECT creator_name, creation_date FROM ai_model_configurations WHERE model_name = 'example_model' ORDER BY creation_date DESC;
SELECT model_id, training_data_source FROM model_metadata WHERE test_data_source = 'test_data_set' AND training_data_source LIKE '%train%';
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM model_parameters WHERE parameter_value > 0.5 ORDER BY parameter_name ASC;
SELECT id, log_date, LEFT(log_message, 50) AS short_message FROM model_logs ORDER BY log_date DESC, id;
SELECT * FROM ai_models;
SELECT model_name, created_at FROM ai_models ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT model_name, model_description FROM ai_models WHERE model_description IS NOT NULL;
SELECT param_name, param_value FROM model_parameters WHERE model_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM evaluation_metrics WHERE metric_value > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM ai_models JOIN model_parameters ON ai_models.model_id = model_parameters.model_id;
SELECT model_name, created_at FROM ai_models WHERE model_name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT * FROM training_data WHERE data_description ILIKE '%example%';
SELECT model_name, param_name, param_value FROM ai_models JOIN model_parameters ON ai_models.model_id = model_parameters.model_id ORDER BY param_name ASC;

SELECT ai_models.model_name, model_parameters.param_name, hyperparam_name FROM ai_models JOIN model_parameters ON ai_models.model_id = model_parameters.model_id LEFT JOIN hyperparameters ON model_parameters.param_id = hyperparameters.param_id;
